This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and semantic parsing. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves machine learning and inference. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves learning algorithms and models. It may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves neural networks and deep learning. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it involves image and video understanding.
